More about Sixt rent a car

Sixt SE is a German multinational car rental company with about 5,000 locations in over 105 countries. Sixt SE acts as a parent and holding company of the Sixt Group, which is internationally active in the business areas of vehicle rental, car sharing, ride-hailing and leasing.
